description: A combination of GANs portaiture and combined with modern digital filtration techniques. The subject was first developed through an A.I. machine and then tweaked with a technique I dubbed 'generative molding,' whereas I use various parameter sliders to mold the image I wish to see from the original generation. From there I will add modern flair and give a futurist fine art bent to my liking.
collection_description: SuperRare makes it easy to create, sell, and collect rare digital art. SuperRare's smart contract platform allows artists to release limited-edition digital artwork tracked on the blockchain, making the pieces rare, verified, and collectible. Filter the crypto art world's best selling works by artist name, creation type, and year of birth on OpenSea.
